                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7188" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0723</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7714 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色羊绒让温暖恒久远：鄂尔多斯集团的可持续商业之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green cashmere makes warmth eternal: Erdos Group&#39;s path to sustainable business</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张术丹，赵云辉，于美鲲，苏日娜，梁宇奇，冯泰文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古鄂尔多斯投资控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鄂尔多斯集团；可持续商业模式；价值创造；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Erdos Group; sustainable business model; value creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">可持续性商业模式是企业以可持续发展为导向，寻求价值主张、价值创造和传递、价值实现的价值创造逻辑，兼顾利益相关方和社会负责任的要求，最终创造出涵盖经济、社会与环境的综合价值与共享价值。鄂尔多斯集团创立至今的40年间，在一个个历史的关键节点上，企业把握机遇，克服困难，经受住了时代的考验，从一家羊绒加工工厂发展成为多元化经营的大型现代综合产业集团，走出了一条可持续商业之路。本案例以鄂尔多斯集团的主要发展阶段为主线，通过对王林祥和王臻两代领导者探索企业发展道路过程的描述，生动地展现出鄂尔多斯集团构建可持续商业模式的具体实践。绿色羊绒真正实现了让温暖恒久远，同时也为同类企业的可持续发展提供了参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Sustainable business is the logic of value creation with sustainable development as the orientation of the enterprise, which seeks value proposition, value creation and transmission, and value realization. It is responsible for stakeholders and society, and ultimately create comprehensive value and shared value covering economy, society and environment. During the 40 years since the establishment of Erdos Group, the company has grasped the opportunities and overcome difficulties at key points in history and withstood the test of the times, it has developed from a cashmere processing factory into a large modern comprehensive industrial group with diversified operations and walking out of a sustainable business path. This case takes the main development stages of Erdos Group as the main line, and through the description of the process of exploring the development path of the enterprise by two generations of leaders, Wang Linxiang and Wang Zhen, it vividly shows the concrete practice of building a sustainable business model in Erdos Group enterprises, it reflects the value creation logic of the enterprise in pursuing the comprehensive value of economy, society and environment and sharing value . Green Cashmere has truly achieved the goal of making warmth eternal, while also providing reference value for the sustainable development of similar enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">可持续商业模式的概念；可持续商业模式的关键要素；可持续商业模式的价值逻辑</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
